Package: ros-hydro-cob-unified-scan-publisher
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, ros-hydro-laser-geometry, ros-hydro-message-filters, ros-hydro-roscpp, ros-hydro-sensor-msgs, ros-hydro-tf
Description: cob_unified_scan_publisher is a tool for unifying two laser scans into a single one. This has shown to provide better results for SLAM than using two laser scanners over a topic relay.
